    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "\ud83c\udfc6 If we ran it ALL on Haiku",
      "description": "Counterfactual: your current Anthropic spend PLUS the Ollama call volume priced at Haiku rates. Shows what local saves you.",
